1.2007</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.32352"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high">Hermopolite</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>κυρίῳ μου <choice><corr>ἀδ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ε</supplied>λφῷ</corr><sic>αδλφω</sic></choice> Νεαρχείδῃ 

    <lb n="2"/>Διοσκουρίδης χαίρειν· 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐξ ὧν ἔγραψεν ὁ πατὴρ Ἱέραξ χάριν 

    <lb n="4"/>ἔχω τῇ <choice><corr>διαθέσει</corr><sic>διαθεσι</sic></choice> σου, <choice><corr>ἀδ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ε</supplied>λφὲ</corr><sic>αδλφε</sic></choice> κύρι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>, 

    <lb n="5"/>ὅτι τὸ σφάλμα ἐβουλήθης διορθώ-

    <lb n="6"/>σασθαι. δέον γάρ σε ἐν τῇ ἀκμῇ τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῆ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> 

    <lb n="7"/>ἐργασίας τὰ καθ᾽ ἡμᾶς ἐν πρώτοις 

    <lb n="8"/>ποιῆσαι γενέσθαι καὶ μὴ προκρίνειν 


    <lb n="9"/>ἄλλους ἡμῶν ἠμέλησας. καὶ νῦν με 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>σφόδρα</corr><sic>σφροδρα</sic></choice> ἐλύπησεν, ὅτι δυσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>ερ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δῶ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="11"/>κατεργάζεται τὰ <hi rend="supraline">ὑ</hi>στερούμενα χώ-

    <lb n="12"/>ματα. καλῶς δὲ <choice><corr>ποιήσεις</corr><sic>ποιησις</sic></choice> καὶ πρε-

    <lb n="13"/>πόντως τῇ εὐγενείᾳ σου, ὅταν 

    <lb n="14"/>τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸ</supplied> πρῶτον σφάλμα διορθώσῃ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ ποιήσῃς κατὰ τρόπον γενέσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θαι</unclear> 

    <lb n="16"/>τὰ ἡμέτερ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> χώμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ατα</unclear>. καὶ <choice><corr>γοῦν</corr><sic>γων</sic></choice> ἀπὸ Δη-

    <lb n="17"/>μητρίου <choice><corr>ἀδ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ε</supplied>λφὸς</corr><sic>αδλφο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear></sic></choice> Νεῖλος ἕωθεν 

    <lb n="18"/>τῆς σήμε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ν, ἥτις ἐστ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὶ</unclear>ν τριακὰς 

    <lb n="19"/>μετὰ τοῦ <choice><corr>ἀδελφοῦ</corr><sic>αδλφου</sic></choice> σου Ὠκεανίου 

    <lb n="20"/>εἰς τὰ <choice><corr>βορεινὰ</corr><sic>βορινα</sic></choice> μέρη ἀπεδήμησεν 

    <lb n="21"/>πρὸ τῆς κομιδῆς τῶν γραμμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ά</unclear>των 

    <lb n="22"/>τοῦ πατρὸς <hi rend="supraline">ι</hi>έρακος. καὶ τῇ νεο-

    <lb n="23"/><subst><add place="inline">μηνίᾳ</add><del rend="corrected">νε<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>μηνια</del></subst> πάντως <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>ραφήσεται αὐτῷ, 

    <lb n="24"/>ὅπως σοι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear>ντίγρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>φα κομισ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ώ</supplied>-

    <lb n="25"/><choice><corr>μεθα</corr><sic>κωμισ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ω</supplied>μεθα</sic></choice> περὶ τοῦ μὴ ἀποσπασθῆ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αι</supplied> 

    <lb n="26"/>τοὺς κωμήτας ἀπὸ τῆς ἐργασίας τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> 

    <lb n="27"/>παρά σοι χωμάτων. <handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σε</unclear> 

    <lb n="28"/>εὔχομαι πολλοῖς χρόνοις 

    <lb n="29"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>ύριε μου <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>δελφέ. </ab></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="301" type="textDate">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Nearchides I. Zur Datierung vgl. Einleitung zu CPR VIII 28 - 43, S. 84 ff.</p></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">CPR</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">28</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">32352</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0009</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">28</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0009;8;28" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">68</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Tafel 13</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.32352" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Hermopolites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>